1. *Radnik* je stigao na posao u sedam ujutro. (The worker arrived at work at 7am.)
2. U ovoj fabrici ima mnogo kvalitetnih *radnika*. (There are many skilled workers in this factory.)
3. Sinoć sam razgovarao sa jednim *radnikom* iz obližnje fabrike. (Last night, I spoke to a worker from a nearby factory.)
4. On je već pet godina *radnik* u ovoj firmi. (He has been an employee of this company for five years already.)
5. *Radniku* je bilo teško da podigne tešku kutiju. (The worker found it difficult to lift the heavy box.)
6. *Radnikom* će upravljati novi menadžer. (The new manager will be in charge of the worker.)
7. On je *radnik* po pozivu. (He is a professional worker.)
8. *Radnik* je dobio povišicu nakon što je napredovao. (The worker received a raise after he was promoted.)
9. U ovoj zgradi žive uglavnom *radnici* i studenti. (Mostly workers and students live in this building.)
10. *Radnici* su organizovali štrajk zbog neisplaćenih plata. (The workers went on strike because their salaries were not paid.)